column5: I'll be meeting someone in International Falls for 5 days of fishing on Wednesday. I was wondering if anyone knew of a good place to leave a vehicle there for 5 days?

Do the same every year and have not had a problem leaving a vehicle at motel we stay at. If your staying overnight, inquire at the motel you'll be staying at...I have not been turned down and have not had a problem on my return. Craig
